Subject: NEA read only access for users
Description: Users are granted read only access in the NEA console, however when trying to open the console the user is presented a message "error code 5. Access denied"
What_We_Know__c:
User has been given permission to access the NEA console, however when trying to start the console the error "error code 5. Access denied" is thrown.
We verified that the user does not have proper permissions applied at the SQL server and needs to be updated
Next_Steps__c: Awaiting customer DB team to create missing permission groups detailed in documentation and customer to test again.
Solution_Comment__c:
Symptom
The customer is trying to setup read only access. Some users are signing in and getting an error when trying to start the console "error code 5. Access denied."

Cause
Users to not have proper permissions to the %SAInstallDir%

Resolution
Added modify access to the %SAInstallDir% and verified uesrs can now start the console and run any functions needed.
